-- China May Link Salary Increases to Consumer Prices, Business News Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-28T01:20:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/china-may-link-salary-increases-to-consumer-prices-business-news-reports.html

          
          
             China may link employee wage
increases to local consumer prices, according to a draft of
salary rules which will be submitted to the State Council soon,
the China Business News reported today, citing Yang Yongqi, a
labor law specialist at the Chinese Academy of Labor Security
Sciences.  
 China may also limit wages for workers at monopoly
industries, Yang was quoted as saying.  
